Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一直戴著那個發飾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…沒什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼理由算是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是沒什麼理由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記帶數學的筆記了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天有數學課嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦  不是還有作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家去取一趟  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正作業也沒做  帶不帶都一樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍然是印尼語早安的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.63,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,300)\fad(600,200)}日\N常\N之\N9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了出現了出現了…麻衣老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這莫非就是必殺技之「招呼保留」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是大氣非凡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像山一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  就像山一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…實際上是不是已經不止山的程度了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  和山是沒有一丁點關係就是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  麻衣生氣的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我昨天把麻衣便當裡的西蘭花吃了的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就買來啦  西蘭花～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了後我才知道麻衣最喜歡西蘭花了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後我一直覺得自己做了不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來也不是西蘭花的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜花？看來也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我做的錯事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道她是為了哪件而生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心裡大概有數
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就只能老實向她道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  昨天吃了你的主菜真對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了兔子蘋果  對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你的飯  對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到只剩黑豆了  對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為昨天午飯的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莫非是更早之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把麻衣抽屜裡放著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒菩薩像的頭折斷的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是之後擅自把佛像帶回家的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是偷偷地把佛像埋進土裡的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:03.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}便條：對不起  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是後來改變主意  在麻衣的桌子上供奉神像的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進一步想想  難道是丟進焚化爐裡燒了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  麻衣你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼啊  原來是在聽音樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你才會不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道  一個人在那裡自言自語地說個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險  差點就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半部分的事  我第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你的髮型  是不是稍微違反了學校裡的風紀規定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃銅鑼燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:16.04,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  還要寫講義  我全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離數學課還有五分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天已經借美緒的作業抄過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一生的請求！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  果然就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀  忘記做數學作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就借我抄一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  Thanks  多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦  我會以超馬赫速度抄完的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  超級大遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西  早上開始就在吵什麼吵  正雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我超級大遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被裁員了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  那個  這個好像和數學講義有些出入…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會請你喝果汁的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課遲到了  老爸也被裁員了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一邊都糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做這種事的時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣正雄豈不是糟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來正雄會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是做這種事的時候啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是生死攸關的時候啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我講義啦  麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這樣了  我會請你吃車站前面的那個的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T…Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  這個  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這不是有的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點拿出來啦  麻衣個壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我就以超快速度開抄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的那張講義  是什麼時候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句話時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題  有沒有會解的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有夠難的啊  赤城的課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記做作業  就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答錯問題的話  又會讓他生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我話講在前面  沒幹勁的傢伙們我會馬上記錄在成績單上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這一招嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會就這麼被你嚇倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.55,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N11
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是23號  我就點座號23號的中之條…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手抽筋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這時候手抽筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  這樣下去的話會進入他視野的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先逃向死角  向死角…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子  椅子被挪動了呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什麼聲音  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有誰的手機響了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信謝禮～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一幕喲  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫做「全班笑得開了花」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個問題  相生你來回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂出喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！  咻啪啪啪啪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻啪啪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:04.52,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N12
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  砂糖和牛奶都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒有忘記買的東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天的雞蛋可真便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我也買了一堆呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了  今天是雞蛋的特賣會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢  雖然還能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是回店裡一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑貓先生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…我不能養你呢  都已經有博士在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  隨便帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…但是好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才不是這個問題呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  難道不可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  可愛是可愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  餵養小動物就要費心去照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你辦的到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不會幫你哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃它的排泄物你也得做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃什麼都不打算幫忙的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就不給你摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！  那…那可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了  不是那個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士  博士  睡著了哦  這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔順哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士好狡猾  我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子的毛也好柔順哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子兩邊也好柔順！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊的肉球好柔順
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊的也好柔順
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴的毛也好柔順！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尾巴  它耳朵裡面的毛才柔順呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  但是摸起來的感覺  尾巴更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴才不柔順呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  是不是哪裡痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了「說話圍巾」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哆啦A夢哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好厲害  但也太快了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快讓阪本戴上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓叫阪本嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  箱子上也這麼寫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  真是廉價的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  戴上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就會說話了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說話喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼想  你們剛才都摸得太過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說  貓會叫個不停幾乎都是因為肚子餓了的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  我不知道這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為箱子上寫著「阪本」  這也太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  我就說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都多少歲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我8歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃的製造年齡是1年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我1歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照人類的年齡來算的話可是有20歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫我「阪本先生」才對頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:18.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大阪腔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  以後能吃到免費的飯我是很感激啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過希望你們能夠謹記對長輩的那份尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句  你們給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定抱有「因為是貓就能隨便摸」這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可說清楚了  雖然我不討厭被隨便摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  貓有著自己的限度…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它放回原來那個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.32,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,270)\fad(600,0)}草\N\N\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來請吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我付了房租還給我吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困難就要互相關照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有別的需要的話  不要客氣  直接說就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  稍微借我點錢…隨便說說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得意忘形的日文是「天狗になる」字面意思就是「變成天狗」…冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  稍微對你好點你就得意忘形了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:45.40,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)\bord10\shad0\be50\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}草\N人\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教…教導主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像誤會什麼了  校長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把它身體的部分打開來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:14.93,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N13
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了的話  車站前的那個就作廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁一局定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready  GO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  麻衣  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你是不是有點搶跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實是有點早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那樣一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧   是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當做沒看見  我們再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重新擺好姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready  GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕視了對手的握力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  這樣一來熱身運動也做夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀  這可真是相當難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  但是我無論身心都開始熱起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該動…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真格的了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我走神了  哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我居然連續三次大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你差不多該…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  是是  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看到了  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初心者的好運就到此為止了哦  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地來決勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  這不是很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫扳手腕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我稍微保管一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久沒有拿出全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我差不多一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不認真的話  我也認真不起來了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  下次才是真真正正的決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要使出必殺技了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個破扳手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變得那麼熱血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  我忘記去上廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺一開始就不怎麼對勁呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  車站前面的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和23瓶果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天手抽筋而且沒有做講義還被罵了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  結果正雄他會怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了啦  我再追加一瓶果汁給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納豆激酶這名  有沒有讓人想吐槽這是什麼笑點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這激酶算什麼啊  是小夜曲嘛
